  "description": "A breathtaking nighttime view of a city skyline illuminated with fireworks. A long bridge stretches across dark water in the foreground, its lights forming a glowing pathway. Beyond the bridge, the city's buildings sparkle with countless lights, creating a dense urban landscape.  Above the city, vibrant fireworks explode in a dazzling display of color, predominantly blue, white, and gold. The fireworks are concentrated towards the left side of the frame. The overall composition captures a sense of celebration and grandeur.",
